        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "5e8c",
          "text": "Anthony Hodgson explores ways of facilitating this transformative response in Ready for Anything — Designing Resilience for a Transforming World (Hodgson, 2011).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
