        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a7de",
          "text": "Hodgson points out that visioning for one-planet living is what we have to do to get ‘ready for anything’ and such visioning is based on three parallel endeavors:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_13",
          "href": null,
          "name": "198a",
          "text": "A creative collective response to the negative challenges in the current situation that could propel us into synchronous failure (eg: the failing of the economy, ecosystems and societies all at once)",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "bb3e",
          "text": "Co-creating a viable and equitable way of one planet living that includes all humanity and the maximum diversity of the biosphere",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a481",
          "text": "Deepening and spreading our understanding of the possible innovative pathways from here to a viable future.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "ULI"
        },
        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1a51",
          "text": "It is important that we learn how to start change within ourselves in order to become more effective change agents in our communities and within our culture. Creating a new vision for our own lives can be the start of a transformative response at the level of the individual.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8a41",
          "text": "More and more people are drawn to a culture of ‘voluntary simplicity’, ‘simple living’, or ‘radical simplicity’. Barabara Max Hubbard, of the Foundation for Conscious Evolution see that the change is primarily an interior one that will then express itself as exterior change through the way we live.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
