        {
          "id": "9c4663f8b0bc_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4626",
          "text": "“We are poised in this critical moment, facing decisions that must be made consciously if we are to avoid destroying the world as we know it, if we are instead to cocreate a future of immeasurable possibilities. Our conscious evolution is an invitation to ourselves, to open to that positive future, to see ourselves as one planet, and to learn to use our powers wisely and ethically for the enhancement of all life on Earth.”— Barbara Max Hubbard, 2012",
